{"lemma":"شَبَحَيْ","slug":"شَبَحَيْ","root":"ش.ب.ح","root_slug":"ش-ب-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ب-ح","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":10,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":16},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n21556","n21558","n21559"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"specter, ghost, apparition, phantom, spirit"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"blurred, indistinct shape","tags":["dated"],"examples":[{"text":"رَأَيْتُ شَبَحًا مِنْ بَعِيدٍ","english":"I saw a shape from afar"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"nightmare"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"one of the 1991–1998 models of a Mercedes-Benz","tags":["Egypt","slang"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"outward appearance, shape, form, figure (of a person)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to appear"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to stand erect (of a person)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of شَبَحَ (šabaḥa, “to appear; to stand erect”) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to extend, to stretch out","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of شَبَحَ (šabaḥa, “to extend, to stretch out”) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"extension, width"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be broad or long in the forearms"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cut, to hew, to pare"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cleave, to split"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of شَبَحَ (šabaḥa, “to cut, to hew; to split”) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be attached to, addicted to, fond of (an affair)"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʃa.baħ/","/ʃabħ/","/ʃa.ba.ħa/","/ʃa.bu.ħa/","/ʃu.bi.ħa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n21556","headword_ar":"شَبُحَ","root":"$bH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$abaAHapN","text_ar":"شَبَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TK,) said of a man, (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, broad in the fore arms:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"long therein."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$abaHahu","text_ar":"شَبَحَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, O, Mgh, L, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aboHN","text_ar":"شَبْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TK,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He extended, stretched,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stretched out, it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, O, Mgh, L, Msb, K;) namely, a thing; (IF, L, Msb;) a hide, or skin, (A, L, K,) or some other thing, (L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between pegs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stakes;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) and a man, (Mgh, L, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between two things, to be flogged,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L,) [i. e.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between two stakes inserted and fixed in the ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb,) which are called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuqaAbaAni","text_ar":"عُقَابَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when he was beaten,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crucified,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like him who is crucified;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$b~Hhu","text_ar":"شبّحهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used, accord. to some, in the same manner. (L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$abaHa yadayohi","text_ar":"شَبَحَ يَدَيْهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He extended,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stretched forth, his arms,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hands:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$abaHa","text_ar":"شَبَحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[alone]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he extended his arm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hand, to offer a prayer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"supplication;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he extended and raised his arms,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hands, in his prayer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"supplication."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHirobaA='u ya$obaHu EalaY AlEuwdi","text_ar":"الحِرْبَا=ءُ يَشْبَحُ عَلَى العُودِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The chameleon extends"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, O)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"itself"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its fore legs"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the branch."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, O.) ―         -b2-  Also, inf. n. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut, hewed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pared, it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a stick, or piece of wood,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as to make it wide."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, L. [See also 2.]) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He clave it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"split it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA,) namely, another's head, or anything whatever. (TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$abaHa lanaA","text_ar":"شَبَحَ لَنَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stood erect"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as though drawing himself up]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to us."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$abaHa laka","text_ar":"شَبَحَ لَكَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appeared,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became apparent, to thee."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ubiHa biA^amorK","text_ar":"شُبِحَ بِاَمْرٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, attached,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"addicted, to an affair;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fond of it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TK","TA","A","O","Mgh","L","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n21558","headword_ar":"شَبْحٌ","root":"$bH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$abaHN","text_ar":"شَبَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places:       -A2-  and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$obuwHN","text_ar":"مَشْبُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n21559","headword_ar":"شَبَحٌ","root":"$bH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, O, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aboHN","text_ar":"شَبْحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$axoSN","text_ar":"شَخْصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"body,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bodily"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corporeal form"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"figure"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"substance, of a man"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"some other thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"object, which one sees from a distance"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, A, O, Msb, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a man,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"some other creature, of which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$axoS","text_ar":"شَخْص"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"body,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appears to one:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing that is perceived by sense"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, O, L) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by sight:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, L:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$obaAHN","text_ar":"اَشْبَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, O, Msb, K,) which is of the former, (A, Msb,) and [of the latter]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ubuwHN","text_ar":"شُبُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laAHa liY $abaHN","text_ar":"لَاحَ لِى شَبَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$axoSN","text_ar":"شَخْصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A body,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bodily form, appeared, loomed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gleamed, to me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humo A^a$obaAHN bilaA A^arowaAHK","text_ar":"هُمْ اَشْبَاحٌ بِلَا اَرْوَاحٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They are bodies without souls"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a*aq~u mino $abaHK","text_ar":"اَذَقُّ مِنْ شَبَحٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baATilK","text_ar":"بَاطِلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, O,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino xayoTi baATilK","text_ar":"مِنْ خَيْطِ بَاطِلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a prov., (O,) meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"More minute,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inconsiderable, than"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the atoms that are seen in the rays of the sun entering from a mural aperture in a chamber:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, * O:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"than the thread that comes forth from the mouth of the spider;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gossamer;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"called by the children"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxaATN","text_ar":"مُخَاطٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~ayoTaAni","text_ar":"الشَّيْطَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^asomaA='u DarobaAni A^asomaA='u A^a$obaAHK","text_ar":"الاَسْمَا=ءُ ضَرْبَانِ اَسْمَا=ءُ اَشْبَاحٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA^asomaA='u A^aEomaAlK","text_ar":"وَاَسْمَا=ءُ اَعْمَالٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Nouns are of two sorts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the names of things perceived by sense, and the names"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of actions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or rather"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of accidents"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attributes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of other things;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as they say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asomaA='u AlA^aEoyaAni","text_ar":"اَسْمَا=ءُ الاَعْيَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asomaA='u AlmaEaAniY","text_ar":"اَسْمَا=ءُ المَعَانِى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"halaka","text_ar":"هَلَكَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$obaAHu maAlihi","text_ar":"اَشْبَاحُ مَالِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The known ones of his camels, and sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats, and other cattle, perished."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K. *)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$abaHN","text_ar":"شَبَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A door"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gate, of high structure;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aboHN","text_ar":"شَبْحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) [but the latter may have originated from a mistranscription; for Sgh says,] and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$abajN","text_ar":"شَبَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O.)       -A3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$abaHapN","text_ar":"شَبَحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","A","O","Msb","K","L"]}]}}